unittitle_ssm: Edward Farbenblum and Orly Lieberman collection of photographs
abstract_ssm: This collection, assembled and donated by Edward Farbenblum and Orly Lieberman, contains New York Theatre and Hollywood Film portraits and production photos dating from 1924-1993, as well as a small amount of ephemera.
